channel.title: PVPOWNAGE! 317 rsps!
channel.description:
My server long description PvP Ownage is back in 317! New Server, Still in Beta Testing, we put the server online so you guys can get a look at the potential and what's to come. Maybe there are even some open staff spots for those handy helpers so come on down get a jump on levels while this server is still in Beta. Currently we're working on adding bosses and teleports to them, fixing bugs and making the server more PvP friendly. Our priority is creating fun for our players, we're very open to suggestions so don't be afraid to contact the owner or myself with suggestions. Welcome to PvP Ownage. DONT FORGET TO SIGN UP ON FORUMS FOR EXTRA FEATURES! NEW SERVER 2ND DAY OPEN!
staff is needed! download here: [url=http://pvpownage.your-talk.com/]http://pvpownage.your-talk.com/[/url]
